FBIS3-15835 "drsov047_t_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-047 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Mar 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Foreign Ministry Acquires 3 Deputy Chancellors WS0903194094 Tallinn BNS in English 1640 GMT 9 Mar 94 WS0903194094 Tallinn BNS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Tallinn, Mar 09, BNS -- Starting from this week, the Estonian Foreign Ministry has three deputy chancellors responsible for different areas of the ministry's activity. Raul Malk, formerly adviser at the ministry, is in charge of the work of the political, information and press departments. Priit Kolbre, who so far headed the ministry's foreign economic policy department, was appointed deputy chancellor for foreign economic policy. The third new appointment is Epp Aruja, former deputy head of the ministry's administrative department, who became deputy chancellor for ministry administration.
